Enron Kids Meeting Please make plans to attend our next Enron Kids meeting on Friday June Noon PM EBC RSVP for lunch required via email by At this meeting officers for this years program will be elected You may nominate people in advance if you wish by replying to this message by May Nominations will also be taken at the meeting The following positions need to be filled Chairperson Vice Chairperson Secretary Treasurer School Liaison TransportationLogistics Cmte Communication Cmte Volunteer Cmte Party Cmte Shopping Cmte

FW Conference Room ReservationsGuys Please review our meeting dates below Let me know if this is ok for now We may have to adjust a bit later on Thanks Lillian Original Message From Villarreal Lillian Sent Tuesday June PM To Facilities Help Desk Subject Conference Room Reservations I need to schedule your Mega conference room for our Enron Kids meetings beginning in July and ending in December Please schedule the following dates from am pm in a Mega conference room Thursday July Thursday August Thursday September Thursday October Thursday November Thursday November Thanksgiving is Thurs Thursday November Thursday December Thursday December Monday December Tuesday December Wednesday we will be busy loading checking and taking the bags to the school Thursday is the party date Please list the contact as Lillian Villarreal xt or Geneva Davis xt Thanks for your help
